name: i want to be a ballet dancer when i grow up necklace
description:
this gorgeous true vintage ballerina is from the 1950s (just think of all the things shes seen!)
she was re-constructed by myself,and is a true one of piece never to be repeated!
from the tip of her fingers to the tip of her pointy toes shes 2 inches in length,and is dangling from a 18" sp chain.
a real delicate but attention grabbing piece

name: here we go round the merry go round necklace
description:
want to relieve your childhood...i dont know about you but i dont think that i ever really left mine behind..but why dont keep a little reminder of those care-free days around your neck!
with real working roundabout
its a 21" chain with true vintage beads
